This paper deals with the convergence analysis of ADMM in deep learning, which is a popular topic in machine learning and computer vision. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, since the paper focuses on the optimization of deep neural networks, cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also a likely sub-category. Finally, since the paper deals with distributed computing, cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possible sub-category as well.
